"Hi Priti, welcome!  It's a pleasure to meet you. Thanks for taking the time to speak with me today.  Your resume shows a strong background in early childhood education, particularly in developing engaging lesson plans and using interactive teaching methods. I'm especially interested in your experience at Auspicious Beginning Pre School and Euro Kids.

To get started, could you please tell me a little about yourself, your background in education, and what interests you most about this opportunity?"
